Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yo, Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau tak ada di ruang merokok di bawah,\N‎jadi aku harus mencari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Semuanya baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Manajer departemen\N‎ingin rapat setelah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:00:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Lagi-lagi rapat yang bisa berlangsung lama\N‎padahal bisa digantikan dengan email…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ayolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku hanya ingin pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau punya kartu poin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya, punya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini kartumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ingin pakai kantong plastik?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yang tiga yen saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Dengan plastik, totalnya 883 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini uangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini kembaliannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Yamada-san dari kasir dua.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Cahayaku di akhir hari kerja yang panjang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tapi…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}‎Aku terlalu sering mampir\N‎bahkan saat aku tak butuh apa pun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}‎Bodoh sekali belanjaanku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Sekalian saja kubelikan Yamada-san hadiah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia mungkin akan suka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Wow! Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Kurasa pria tua yang suka berkhayal\N‎sepertikulah yang buat situasi canggung.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ada apa denganmu, Sasaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau tiba-tiba lupa bahwa mengunjungi klien\N‎bukan jalan-jalan santai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Astaga. Kau harus memberitahuku\N‎soal hal-hal seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maafkan aku, Pak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bicaralah, Sasaki-kun!\N‎Ingatlah untuk bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku akan dipertanyakan\N‎apa pantas mengelola…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Pak. Maaf mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Eda dari Perusahaan Square\N‎bertanya tentang penawaran harga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Katakan akan kami jawab besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf membuatmu menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya. Akan siap besok. Ya. Maaf…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Rapat pukul tujuh malam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Atasan bodoh itu…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tak hanya bekerja sampai tengah malam,\N‎tapi juga tak ada yang terpecahkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Akan kubunuh{\i0}‎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tidak jadi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Pada saat seperti ini…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Apalagi di saat seperti ini…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Aku butuh Yamada-san malam ini!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini kembaliannya, Sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Yamada-san pasti sedang libur\N‎atau sudah pulang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Hari ini semuanya tak berjalan\N‎sesuai rencana.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Kumohon, Nikotin.\N‎Jangan mengecewakanku hari ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎- Menjijikkan.\N‎- Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Jangan bilang tak ada area merokok?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sejak kapan para perokok\N‎kehilangan haknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Hei, Om.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sebelah sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Merokoklah bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Menarik sekali{\i0}‎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tunggu, bukankah ini\N‎di belakang supermarket?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tak kena masalah\N‎kau biarkan orang luar merokok di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Siapa yang akan tahu\N‎kau orang luar atau bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kalau begitu, aku akan ikut merokok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tak yakin apa komunitasnya,\N‎tapi dia terlihat intens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tak terlihat dia bekerja di sini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jadi, Nona, kau bekerja di supermarket\N‎bagian apa…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ayo, nyalakan rokokku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Untuk apa lagi aku memanggilmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Seharusnya kau bilang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku hanya bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jangan bercanda dengan orang\N‎yang baru kau temui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau orang yang selalu mengantre\N‎di kasir dua, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku? Pasti kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa juga kebetulan kau mengantre di sana\N‎bahkan saat kasir lain kosong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia tahu rutinitasku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau suka Yamada-san, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia sudah tahu jawabannya,\N‎tapi tetap menggodaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yamada-san gadis yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Cantik dan berdada besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Dan dia lajang, pasti kau senang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Itu tak benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya, aku tahu aku pria aneh\N‎yang suka mengantre di kasir Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi sejujurnya, etos kerjanyalah\N‎yang membuatku bersemangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Cuma itu yang membuatku "senang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku agak kelewatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎- Syukurlah.\N‎- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kupikir Yamada-san\N‎dapat pelanggan berengsek lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Banyak orang idiot yang mengganggunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi kau tak seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bekerja keraslah\N‎dan jaga sikapmu, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Kupikir dia hanya wanita muda tak sopan\N‎yang jahil pada pria yang lebih tua,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎tapi sepertinya dia anak baik\N‎yang menjaga temannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf, tapi kau harus bayar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sasaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Hah? Bagaimana kau tahu namaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku sudah lama tahu namamu\N‎dari kartu poinmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku ingin berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku sudah bicara dengan Tayama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎- Aku senang mendengarnya.\N‎- Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Dia bilang kau penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kartumu jatuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Sial, Tayama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Akan kuingat nama itu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yo. Aku Tayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sampai jumpa di area merokok, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jika dipikir, bagaimana Tayama-san\N‎tahu namaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Rapat lagi sampai tengah malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Semoga ada yang mengamuk\N‎di rapat untuk kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Rapat ini, rapat itu. Rapat tentang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Semua orang tegang\N‎karena rapat yang tak ada hentinya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Bahkan aku…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tapi aku punya penyemangat terbaik!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Senyum Yamada-san dari kasir dua Super S!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Selamat datang! Terima kasih banyak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Kau orang yang selalu mengantre\N‎di kasir nomor dua, 'kan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia tak ada di sini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Waktunya pas sekali!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia bilang kau penggemarku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Baiklah. Kau punya kartu poin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎- Punya.\N‎- Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini kartumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Aku sudah bicara dengan Tayama-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia bilang kau penggemarku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Pak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Totalnya 883 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Kuperlihatkan diriku sebagai idiot\N‎yang menjijikkan dan kikuk,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎tapi aku senang dia tetap\N‎melayaniku dengan sopan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Hanya aku yang menjadi aneh soal ini!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Bodoh! Idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Mulai sekarang, aku akan\N‎belanja dengan diam-diam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Lakukan sesukamu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}‎Klien itu masih belum menghubungiku\N‎setelah kukirim permintaan maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}‎Aku akan mati tanpa pernah\N‎melihat keluargaku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Di samping pria tua ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bisa hentikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Lagi pula, kenapa kau lembur hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku memperbaiki berkas\N‎yang dibuat karyawan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau biarkan mereka memanfaatkanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tidak, pekerjaan seperti ini\N‎tak seharusnya dikerjakan karyawan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Manajer departemen, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎"Berikan masalah kepada mereka.\N‎Begitulah cara terbaik untuk belajar."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Lalu dia suruh orang lain\N‎membereskan kekacauan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi para karyawan baru\N‎yang paling kasihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku bisa tahu dari berkas ini\N‎mereka bersungguh-sungguh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Selain itu… Aku punya penyemangat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Selamat datang!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Ini bukan apa-apa jika aku tahu bisa…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Oh? Pak Penggemar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku menghapus semua pembaruanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini pantas dirayakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Dia tak di sini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Seolah-olah alam semesta bilang,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎"Rasakan, Sasaki, akibat mencari\N‎penghiburan dari orang lain."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Aku benar-benar harus cari hobi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa kabar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tempat merokoknya kosong, kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ingin merokok juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tayama-san! Ada yang ingin\N‎kubicarakan denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bisa-bisanya kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau bilang pada Yamada-san\N‎aku penggemarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sekarang aku terlalu malu\N‎mengantre di kasirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi kau tetap mengantre di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Bagaimana kau melihat itu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Maaf karena menyebalkan, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi Yamada-san senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Dia bilang sendiri, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:18:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku bukan anak kecil\N‎yang mudah percaya. Kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Hanya itu yang ingin kau bicarakan padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Dan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ucapan terima kasih karena telah\N‎membiarkanku merokok denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Hei, bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau tahu itu? "Kerupuk Beras Lezat."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku suka itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini populer di antara orang tua, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Apa aku setua itu baginya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku sudah lama ingin mencoba ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terima kasih, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jangan berdiri saja. Merokoklah bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Oh? Dia suka hadiah dari orang tua?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Tayama-san. Kau suka sesuatu\N‎yang sedang tren lagi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku agak lapar setelah bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jangan makan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jangan makan berlebihan sebelum tidur…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Rokokku tertinggal di kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku tak punya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini. Bisa isap punyaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku tak bisa menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ambillah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jika karena kau ingin makan kerupuknya,\N‎katakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Wow, Sasaki-san. Kau peka sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau suka menjahili pria tua, Tayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sangat suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Pasti itu seru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bisa salahkan aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau seperti penghilang stresku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa? Penghilang stres?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Seperti kau mengantre di kasir Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau menggodaku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tak sepertimu,\N‎aku tak menjahili Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau tak mengerti, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kita semua punya cara berbeda\N‎untuk hilangkan stres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jadi, jangan cemberut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sampai jumpa lagi, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku tak cemberut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bagaimana kliennya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya. Aku ahlinya minta maaf,\N‎jadi semua sudah teratasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa kerupuk beras ini darimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Bagaimana kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau bodoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Sudah berapa kali kau membuatku makan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Begitu mulai, tak cukup satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ini cocok dengan alkohol.\N‎Bawalah pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Akan kubawa pulang! Sebungkus penuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi kenapa kau punya banyak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau beli banyak sekaligus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku selalu beli itu saat ke supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Aku lupa kalau sudah beli,\N‎jadi sekarang aku punya banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa? Kalau begitu, jangan beli lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi aku jadi tak punya alasan\N‎untuk ke supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kalau begitu, berhenti ke supermaket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Jangan beli itu lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau selalu beli ini. Ini lezat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kau juga suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tapi hanya baru-baru ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Ada yang memberikannya padaku\N‎dan ternyata itu enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tak cukup hanya satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Seseorang memberikannya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Kerupuk berasnya enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Apa mungkin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Apa Yamada-san dan Tayama-san{\i0}‎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‎Mereka pasti teman dekat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Cobalah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Wow. Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Yamada-chan. Kau punya alergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Mungkin cuma pria tua tak peka\N‎yang berkhayal tentangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‎Terjemahan subtitle oleh Rahayu Kinasih
